seo: JsFind,接口提取,GET请求,POST请求,状态码统计
seo_en: JsFind,API extraction,GET request,POST request,status code statistics
summary: 该插件用于快速提取JS文件中的接口，并自动发送GET和POST请求，同时统计不同状态码的响应数量。
summary_en: This plugin is used to quickly extract APIs from JS files, automatically send GET and POST requests, and count the number of responses with different status codes.
